name: Sweventel • Raze Hell
description: Entoptic visions, remnants of the archane psyche...dreams, gateway to the cosmic mind and alternate instances of the soul, existence in many worlds... echoes, as the doom tellers foretold, awaiting the sign of the eschaton... a soul unconquered is wagered to reckon the damned, raze hell and claim bounty… first, foremost and final, the astral warrior, Atummia Mammen. 1920 x 1080
